lyric: Here I feel the touch brought by the real number solution.
translation: 我感受到了实数解的触碰

lyric: Ripples of two souls now have reached our double slits.
translation: 两个灵魂的涟漪已到达属于我们的那对狭缝

lyric: Casting stripes of light and dark in the world as days and nights.
translation: 在这世界投射出明暗条带，作为日夜更迭

lyric: You set me free under the sun.
I fly your cradle dreams to the moon and back.
translation: 我倾愿放飞你的襁褓之梦

lyric: A worm will turn into a butterfly,
before one can answer "who am I".
translation: 在一个人能找到自我之前

lyric: After the ice turns into water,
the sea I hang upside down will be your sky.
translation: 我倒悬过来的海会成为你的天
